<h2>TIME AWAY FROM NOODLE</h2>

<p>Paid Time Off
To stay focused and maintain the energy to pursue our goals, it’s important to get away from the office and clear your mind once in a while. There are also times when we must balance needs outside the workplace. Full-time salaried employees earn Paid Time Off (“PTO”).</p>

<p>PTO includes sick time, vacations, holidays (other than those observed by Noodle Education, Inc.), and most other days away from the office that are not work-related. A single PTO approach to time away promotes flexibility, but requires you to manage your time for the unexpected. We all want time to unwind, be sure to leave enough time for illness, appointments, emergencies, or other needs that require time off from work.</p>

<p>Here’s the accrual schedule:</p>


